	<p>Robert L. Nefsky leads our Firm's insurance practice. He is a member of the Federation of Regulatory Counsel (FORC), a national association of insurance attorneys with members in all states and major cities; and a member of the International Association of Insurance Receivers (IAIR), an international organization promoting competency and integrity in the receivership of insurance companies, and regularly attends NAIC meetings.</p>
